      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KYVALLEY JETSTREAM NZ (4) added to a string of wins and placings at the latest appearance when he got the job done again, scoring by a neck at this circuit and distance. That took his record here to three from five. Can strike again. IRON WOMEN (3) drew wider and worked when resuming but will be better for that outings. Tackled the good fillies last season and goes well at this distance. Improver from a good draw. NO MONEY NO HONEY (2) was well fancied when resuming but manners let her down. Has the benefit of a good draw and is proven second-up so she is worth another chance. HEZA GUN (7) draws wide but hasn't been far away of late including a placing here last start. RAPID RETURN (5) draws wider but is heading the right way, improving last time out for a 1.5m second at this venue.",
